{"text": "Great game! there are so many posibilites for this rpg, we did wait long for this and finally its out! And it SUCKS, mostly because ubisoft sucks and opens every door for hackers and glitch-user, like 30% of the players are hacking and u cant even find players to play normal missions with u, cause everyone just uses glitches. Not much late game content, not much to do besides shooting mobs in DZ all day and get shot by hackers from time to time. Besides this major problems im even disappointed by social system or/and reporting system. Way to annoying u cant report ingame, or a whisper function in the friendlist or something similar would be nice. And Ubisoft seems like theres no problem, just keep releaseing new missions which are easy to glitch and that will fix everything... Also, on a side note, american players get bonus items, europe accounts cant achive because they sold it more often there. Well okay, but why the hell we get on the same servers if they got an advantage anyway??  No sense in this, but well doesnt matter cause all in all u cant play pvp for more than 3 minutes without beeing killed by hackers anyway, so â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ it. Otherwise i would have really loved the game, i may even keep playing, cause i got still a little bit faith in the game. Even if it feels like hammerpoints WarZ/Infestation right now.", "appid": "365590", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971224911", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461412800.0}
