{"text": "I wont lie, the game is absolutely gorgeous. It runs well, and havent encountered any bugs. The problem for me is the price. 54,99â‚¬ - Thats the price you pay for triple A masterpieces like Witcher 3, Red Dead Redemtion 2, Cyberpunk 2077. This game is not a triple A masterpiece, and it has nowhere near the depth you'd expect a 55â‚¬ game to have. On top of that it is still just a park builder/park manager game. The price is absolutely ridiculous. Save those 55â‚¬ for Red Dead Redemption 2 or Cyberpunk 2077. This is a 25$ game at MOST. 55â‚¬ is ridiculous. It is a good game nonetheless, but not worth the money. Wait for a BIG sale.", "appid": "648350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008089686", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528804800.0}
